message.body: crazy. i felt today like you did last week. how're you?
Pretty great, figured out the perfect Saturday hangover cure: spend all day in the sun at a beer and pizza picnic.
i did pizza and wine indoors. also lotsss of sleep. so i'm close to your level, haha.
Hahaha, but you didn't get the lovely sunburn ;) What's your week looking like?
busy. :/ i'm free thursday afternoon and most of saturday, though.
Hmmm, lets shoot for thur, but I might have a work thing come up.
